India and China will be the superpowers in 50-100 years, because they're the only countires with population and intellectual advantage.<br>
US has a better ally in India then China.<br>
Russia has a better ally in India then China...even when they had the same ideology, Russia and china couldn't get along that well.<br>
United States is not going to stay at the top for a long time. It's geography has enabled it to remain isolated and develope a nice economy. But, there is a limit to US advantage.<br>
<br>
Also, Islam's repressive nature and China's repressive nature make them ideal allies. The US war on terror will eventually turn into a war on Islam, and China will take the side of Islam, and there you have world war three planned out very nicely.<br>
<br>
